{"tid":1928154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再有留英港生疑染疫 院方拒做測試求助無門","createTime":"2020-03-16T08:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T08:48:32.000Z","uid":80516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33489982adf7b5370d5d3992e249369eef31751d","tid":1928154,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"再有留英港生疑染疫 院方拒做測試求助無門<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=16cddd18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】歐洲國家的新冠肺炎疫情嚴峻，有議員再收到於英國留學的香港學生求助，兩名留學生分別在倫敦和曼徹斯特，亦有出現新冠肺炎病徵，但未能得到治療。<span style=\"color: red;\">另有留學生指，當地人防疫意識低，多數都沒戴口罩，若戴口罩會遭受歧視</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員葛珮帆指，其中一名女事主在倫敦求學，她上周二(10日)開始咳嗽、發低燒，同住的室友、老師等人亦出現類似病徵，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾致電私家診所求助，惟因涉及新冠肺炎被拒絕求診，求醫無門，即使致電當地專線尋求協助亦未得到回覆</span>，十分無助。<br />\n<br />\n第二宗的男事主現位於曼徹斯特，<span style=\"color: red;\">他出現發高燒和咳嗽，曾赴醫院求醫，但醫生未有為其配藥和檢測，只叫他自我隔離。</span>葛引述該名男學生表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">目前英國的情況十分危險，不論是醫院或街上的人多數都沒戴口罩，他在醫院求醫時戴口罩更遭受歧視，直斥當地防疫意識甚低，又不為懷疑個案進行病毒測試</span>，相信有一定數量的受感染人士未有確診，但持續在社區活動，情況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n她又引述留學生指，<span style=\"color: red;\">身邊的同學和朋友亦相繼出現病徵，都沒有進行病毒檢測，未能證實自己是否已染疫，當地很多留學港生都已經購買機票提早回港</span>。<br />\n<br />\n葛表示，接獲求助後已即時將個案轉介相關部門和入境處，尋求中國駐英國大使館協助。她憂慮香港近日輸入確診個案不斷上升，相繼錄得來自英國、美國、印度等的輸入個案，要求港府對有關入境者進行14天強制家居隔離及醫學監測，亦應考慮禁止過去14天曾到意大利及西班牙等大爆發地區的海外人士入境香港，嚴防病毒「入口」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200315/bkn-20200315164424645-0315_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200315%2Fbkn-20200315164424645-0315_00822_001.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=d1948a0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200315/bkn-20200315164424645-0315_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"60482d65cd8968af603906aa12bc9bd9410c1c67","tid":1928154,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15a8be6cd70663df865f43f81db640b6bcce1cd","tid":1928154,"uid":174432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"點解好搵唔搵搵聞便聯？"},{"pid":"ce28e19644db99ab7131f96709417a598e8a0626","tid":1928154,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60482d65cd8968af603906aa12bc9bd9410c1c67","tid":1928154,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ee599035009d67d9272a24f17a5d8e2283430d","tid":1928154,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"仲唔搵民主黨公民黨幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11a7d46b53429d3ddffae7ad4e0de989e392b89","tid":1928154,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15a8be6cd70663df865f43f81db640b6bcce1cd","tid":1928154,"uid":174432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"點解好搵唔搵搵聞便聯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"5aead9e032eb38b1dc12c3922dd99e53849c39da","tid":1928154,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b11a7d46b53429d3ddffae7ad4e0de989e392b89","tid":1928154,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15a8be6cd70663df865f43f81db640b6bcce1cd","tid":1928154,"uid":174432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08: